1
0:00:12.49,000 --> 0:00:16,000
I'd like to tell you today about an orca named Tahlequah.

2
0:00:17.361,000 --> 0:00:2,000
Tahlequah is also known as J35 to scientists,

3
0:00:21.258,000 --> 0:00:24,000
