19
0:01:20.754,000 --> 0:01:23,000
and scientists were so excited by this development.

20
0:01:24.691,000 --> 0:01:27,000
But unfortunately, the same day -- in fact, shortly after birth --

21
0:01:28.69,000 --> 0:01:29,000
