48
0:02:53.287,000 --> 0:02:55,000
And part of the reason, I think,

49
0:02:55.464,000 --> 0:02:57,000
is because of what I call the "a-word."

50
0:02:58.592,000 --> 0:02:59,000
The a-word is anthropomorphism,

51
0:03:00.375,000 --> 0:03:02,000
and historically, it's been a big deterrent

52
0:03:02.4,000 --> 0:03:04,000
