104
0:05:27.038,000 --> 0:05:28,000
over the body.

105
0:05:28.664,000 --> 0:05:3,000
So the scientists watching the elephants

106
0:05:31.191,000 --> 0:05:34,000
kept close observation on Eleanor's body

