137
0:07:05.888,000 --> 0:07:06,000
and he was.

138
0:07:07.341,000 --> 0:07:09,000
But then the sanctuary workers did a brilliant thing,

139
0:07:09.952,000 --> 0:07:12,000
because they brought Harper to the body to see.

140
0:07:14.015,000 --> 0:07:17,000
And at first, Harper prodded the body of his friend,

141
0:07:17.074,000 --> 0:07:2,000
but then he laid himself over it,

142
0:07:20.327,000 --> 0:07:23,000
and he stayed there for over an hour with his friend.

143
0:07:23.996,000 --> 0:07:25,000
And in the weeks after,

144
0:07:26.961,000 --> 0:07:27,000
he had a hard time.

145
0:07:28.681,000 --> 0:07:31,000
He would go back to that same pond where he had been with Kohl,

146
0:07:31.853,000 --> 0:07:33,000
and he didn't want any other friends.

147
0:07:34.536,000 --> 0:07:36,000
And within two months, he died as well.

148
0:07:38.307,000 --> 0:07:39,000
Now, I'm happy to say

149
0:07:39.637,000 --> 0:07:42,000
