0:10:06.75,000 --> 0:10:08,000
and she then slowly recovered.

199
0:10:11.055,000 --> 0:10:13,000
So we have bereaved baboons.

200
0:10:13.918,000 --> 0:10:16,000
Will science tell us someday about bereaved bees?

